      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and there\u2019s not a single blemish to be found. If you're looking for perfection, this is it. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
