    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-quality condition. This example is powered by the legendary S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS, which has been recently overhauled with Beisan components. The subframe has been proactively reinforced with structural plates, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains rigid and corrosion-free, supported by a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers and OEM bushings. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic with factory-spec paint depth and an immaculate Nappa leather interior, this M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal performance.",
      "price": 47500.0,
